---
layout: base
lang: "es"
title: "Eventos | Cortney Peterson para el Congreso — OH-11"
description: "Próximos eventos de campaña de Cortney Peterson para el Congreso — asambleas, recorridos de puertas, bancos telefónicos y reuniones comunitarias en el Distrito Congresional 11 de Ohio."
ogTitle: "Eventos | Cortney Peterson para el Congreso"
ogDescription: "Asambleas, recorridos de puertas, bancos telefónicos y reuniones comunitarias para la campaña de Cortney Peterson en el Distrito 11 de Ohio."
ogUrl: "https://cortneyforcongress.org/es/events.html"
navActive: "events"
pageScripts: ["events.js"]
hreflang:
  - lang: en
    url: https://cortneyforcongress.org/events.html
  - lang: es
    url: https://cortneyforcongress.org/es/events.html
  - lang: x-default
    url: https://cortneyforcongress.org/events.html
permalink: /es/events.html
ldJson: false
pageStyle: >
  /* FILTER BAR */
  .filter-bar{background:var(--white);border-bottom:1px solid var(--cream-dark);padding:1rem 1.5rem;position:sticky;top:62px;z-index:100}
  .filter-inner{max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:0.6rem;flex-wrap:wrap}
  .filter-label{font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif;font-size:0.75rem;letter-spacing:0.2em;color:var(--text-light);text-transform:uppercase;margin-right:0.25rem}
  .filter-btn{padding:0.4rem 1rem;border-radius:50px;border:1.5px solid var(--cream-dark);background:transparent;color:var(--text-light);font-size:0.82rem;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;transition:all 0.2s;font-family:'Source Sans 3',sans-serif;letter-spacing:0.03em;min-height:44px}
  .filter-btn:hover,.filter-btn.active{background:var(--plum);color:var(--white);border-color:var(--plum)}
  /* EVENT CARDS */
  .events-grid{display:grid;gap:1.25rem;margin-top:2rem}
  .event-card{background:var(--white);border-radius:16px;border:1.5px solid var(--cream-dark);overflow:hidden;display:grid;grid-template-columns:auto 1fr auto;align-items:center;gap:0;transition:border-color 0.3s,box-shadow 0.3s}
  .event-card:hover{border-color:var(--coral);box-shadow:0 6px 24px rgba(71,13,68,0.1)}
  .event-date-block{background:var(--plum);color:var(--white);padding:1.25rem 1.5rem;text-align:center;min-width:90px;align-self:stretch;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center}
  .event-month{font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif;font-size:0.85rem;letter-spacing:0.2em;color:var(--coral-light);text-transform:uppercase}
  .event-day{font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif;font-size:2.5rem;line-height:1;color:var(--white)}
  .event-dow{font-size:0.75rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.1em;margin-top:0.1rem}
  .event-body{padding:1.25rem 1.5rem}
  .event-type-tag{display:inline-block;font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif;font-size:0.75rem;letter-spacing:0.2em;padding:0.2rem 0.6rem;border-radius:4px;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:0.5rem}
  .tag-town-hall{background:#e8f4e8;color:#2d6a2d}
  .tag-canvass{background:#fff3e0;color:#a05000}
  .tag-phone-bank{background:#e8eaf6;color:#3949ab}
  .tag-fundraiser{background:#fce4ec;color:#ad1457}
  .tag-community{background:#e0f7fa;color:#006064}
  .tag-rally{background:#f3e5f5;color:#6a1b9a}
  .event-title{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:1.15rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--plum);line-height:1.3;margin-bottom:0.4rem}
  .event-meta{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:0.75rem;font-size:0.83rem;color:var(--text-light)}
  .event-meta span{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:0.3rem}
  .event-desc{font-size:0.9rem;color:var(--text-light);margin-top:0.6rem;line-height:1.6}
  .event-actions{padding:1.25rem 1.5rem;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0.6rem;min-width:130px}
  .btn-rsvp{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;padding:0.6rem 1.25rem;background:var(--plum);color:var(--white);border-radius:8px;text-decoration:none;font-weight:700;font-size:0.82rem;letter-spacing:0.05em;text-transform:uppercase;transition:all 0.25s;white-space:nowrap}
  .btn-rsvp:hover{background:var(--coral-light);transform:translateY(-1px)}
  .btn-details{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;padding:0.6rem 1.25rem;background:transparent;color:var(--plum);border:1.5px solid var(--plum);border-radius:8px;text-decoration:none;font-weight:700;font-size:0.82rem;letter-spacing:0.05em;text-transform:uppercase;transition:all 0.25s;white-space:nowrap}
  .btn-details:hover{background:var(--plum);color:var(--white)}
  /* NO EVENTS STATE */
  .no-events{text-align:center;padding:4rem 2rem;background:var(--white);border-radius:16px;border:2px dashed var(--cream-dark);margin-top:2rem}
  .no-events p{color:var(--text-light);font-size:1rem}
  /* PAST EVENTS */
  .past-section{background:var(--white)}
  .past-list{list-style:none;margin-top:1.75rem;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0.75rem}
  .past-item{display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:1rem;font-size:0.92rem;padding:0.6rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06)}
  .past-item:last-child{border-bottom:none}
  .past-date{font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif;font-size:0.82rem;letter-spacing:0.15em;color:var(--coral);white-space:nowrap;min-width:90px;font-weight:700}
  .past-title{color:var(--text-light)}
  .past-location{color:var(--text-light);font-style:italic;font-size:0.85rem}
  /* HOST CTA */
  .host-cta{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--plum-deep),var(--plum));padding:5rem 1.5rem;text-align:center;color:var(--white)}
  .host-cta-inner{max-width:640px;margin:0 auto}
  .host-cta h2{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:clamp(1.8rem,4vw,2.5rem);font-weight:900;margin-bottom:1rem}
  .host-cta p{font-size:1.05rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.8);margin-bottom:2rem;line-height:1.7}
  /* RESPONSIVE */
  @media(max-width:767px){
    .event-card{grid-template-columns:auto 1fr;grid-template-rows:1fr auto}
    .event-actions{grid-column:1/-1;flex-direction:row;padding:0 1.25rem 1.25rem;border-top:1px solid var(--cream-dark)}
    .event-date-block{grid-row:1/2}
    .filter-bar{padding:0.75rem 1rem;overflow-x:auto;-webkit-overflow-scrolling:touch}
    .filter-inner{flex-wrap:nowrap;gap:0.5rem}
    .filter-btn{flex-shrink:0;font-size:0.8rem;padding:0.35rem 0.8rem}
    .events-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr !important}
    .host-cta{padding:4rem 1.25rem}
  }
  @media(max-width:480px){
    .event-card{grid-template-columns:1fr;grid-template-rows:auto}
    .event-date-block{flex-direction:row;gap:0.5rem;align-items:baseline;padding:0.9rem 1.25rem;justify-content:flex-start}
    .event-day{font-size:1.6rem}
    .event-actions{flex-direction:column;gap:0.75rem}
    .filter-inner{gap:0.4rem}
    .filter-bar{padding:0.5rem}
    .host-cta{padding:3rem 1rem}
    .host-cta h2{font-size:1.6rem}
  }
  @media(min-width:768px) and (max-width:1023px){
    .events-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}
    .host-cta{padding:5rem 2rem}
  }
  @media(min-width:1024px){
    .host-cta{padding:7rem 3rem}
    .events-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}
  }
---

<main id="main-content">
<!-- HERO DE LA PÁGINA -->
<header class="page-hero">
  <div class="page-hero-inner">
    <p class="page-label">En el Terreno</p>
    <h1><em>Eventos</em> de Campaña</h1>
    <p>Asambleas, recorridos de puertas, bancos telefónicos y reuniones comunitarias en todo el Distrito 11 de Ohio. Participa. Marca la diferencia.</p>
  </div>
</header>

<!-- BARRA DE FILTROS -->
<div class="filter-bar" role="search" aria-label="Filtrar eventos por tipo">
  <div class="filter-inner">
    <span class="filter-label">Filtrar:</span>
    <button class="filter-btn active" data-filter="all" aria-pressed="true">Todos los Eventos</button>
    <button class="filter-btn" data-filter="town-hall" aria-pressed="false">Asambleas</button>
    <button class="filter-btn" data-filter="canvass" aria-pressed="false">Recorridos</button>
    <button class="filter-btn" data-filter="phone-bank" aria-pressed="false">Bancos Telefónicos</button>
    <button class="filter-btn" data-filter="rally" aria-pressed="false">Manifestaciones</button>
    <button class="filter-btn" data-filter="community" aria-pressed="false">Comunitarios</button>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- PRÓXIMOS EVENTOS -->
<section class="section" aria-labelledby="upcoming-heading">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <p class="section-label">No Te Lo Pierdas</p>
    <h2 class="section-title" id="upcoming-heading">Próximos <em>Eventos</em></h2>

    <div class="events-grid" id="eventsGrid" aria-live="polite">

      {%- set hasUpcoming = false %}
      {%- for event in events %}
        {%- if event.date | isFuture %}
          {%- set hasUpcoming = true %}
      <article class="event-card reveal" data-type="{{ event.type }}"
        data-cal-title="{{ event.title }}"
        data-cal-start="{{ event.date | icsDateTime(event.startTime) }}"
        data-cal-end="{{ event.date | icsDateTime(event.endTime) }}"
        data-cal-location="{{ event.location }}"
        data-cal-desc="{{ event.descriptionEs or event.description }}">
        <div class="event-date-block">
          <span class="event-month">{{ event.date | eventMonth }}</span>
          <span class="event-day">{{ event.date | eventDay }}</span>
          <span class="event-dow">{{ event.date | eventDowEs }}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="event-body">
          <span class="event-type-tag tag-{{ event.type }}">{{ event.type | eventTypeEs }}</span>
          <h3 class="event-title">{{ event.title }}</h3>
          <div class="event-meta">
            <span><svg aria-hidden="true" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="vertical-align:-2px;margin-right:3px"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/></svg>{{ event.startTime | formatTime }}{% if event.endTime %} – {{ event.endTime | formatTime }}{% endif %}</span>
            <span><svg aria-hidden="true" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="vertical-align:-2px;margin-right:3px"><path d="M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z"/><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/></svg>{{ event.location }}</span>
          </div>
          <p class="event-desc">{{ event.descriptionEs or event.description }}</p>
        </div>
        <div class="event-actions">
          <button class="btn-add-cal" onclick="addToCal(this)" aria-label="Agregar al calendario">
            <svg aria-hidden="true" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"/><line x1="16" y1="2" x2="16" y2="6"/><line x1="8" y1="2" x2="8" y2="6"/><line x1="3" y1="10" x2="21" y2="10"/></svg>
            Agregar al Calendario
          </button>
          <a href="/es/get-involved.html" class="btn-rsvp">Participa</a>
        </div>
      </article>
        {%- endif %}
      {%- endfor %}

    </div><!-- end eventsGrid -->

    {%- if not hasUpcoming %}
    <div class="no-events">
      <p>No hay eventos programados en este momento.<br>Síguenos en redes sociales para anuncios, o <a href="/es/get-involved.html" style="color:var(--coral);font-weight:700">regístrate para participar</a>.</p>
    </div>
    {%- endif %}
  </div>
</section>

<!-- EVENTOS PASADOS -->
<section class="section past-section" aria-labelledby="past-heading">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <p class="section-label">Estuvimos Ahí</p>
    <h2 class="section-title" id="past-heading">Eventos <em>Pasados</em></h2>
    <ul class="past-list" aria-label="Eventos pasados de la campaña">
      {%- for event in events %}
        {%- if event.date | isPast %}
      <li class="past-item" data-type="{{ event.type }}">
        <span class="past-date">{{ event.date | eventReadable }}</span>
        <span class="past-title">{{ event.descriptionEs or event.title }} &nbsp;<span class="past-location">{{ event.location }}</span></span>
      </li>
        {%- endif %}
      {%- endfor %}
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ORGANIZA UN EVENTO CTA -->
<section class="host-cta" aria-labelledby="host-heading">
  <div class="host-cta-inner">
    <p class="page-label" style="color:var(--coral-light)">Hazlo Realidad</p>
    <h2 id="host-heading">Organiza un Evento para Cortney</h2>
    <p>¿Tienes espacio, un vecindario, un salón sindical o un patio trasero? Nosotros vamos a ti. Las fiestas en casa y los eventos comunitarios son como las campañas populares ganan.</p>
    <div class="btn-group">
      <a href="/es/get-involved.html" class="btn btn-coral">Regístrate para Organizar</a>
      <a href="{{ site.donateUrl }}" class="btn btn-ghost" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Apoya la Campaña</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</main>
